{
  "texts": [
    "He had come to Nineveh to offer them a chance at redemption, but he wasn't sure if that was enough.",
    "He wasn't sure if God's mercy was enough.",
    "As the men sat at Jonah's feet, listening to his words, Jonah realized that he had been wrong.",
    "He had been so focused on the wrongs of Nineveh that he had forgotten about the rights.",
    "He had been so focused on the judgment that he had forgotten about the mercy."
  ]
}